{
  "stem": "25114.7",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And we-- we-- by this time, the capital of the part of Poland which was liberated was Lublin.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So we were heading for Lublin.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We had papers-- everything.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And we got stuck in a town before Lublin, I think-- I think 30 kilometers or something, or 60 kilometers.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I can't remember [? now ?].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "In a place called-- in a town called Chelm.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And we slept over there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "We couldn't get into Lublin, because it was-- the lines were broken.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Right through.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "You had to wait, stop, and wait for the lines to be repaired, and stop.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And that's why it lasted so long.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Because the lines were-- they were bombed [? or ?] destroyed.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So there was no time to-- you know, we were on our last, really, leg, as they say.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the men had a-- couple of men had a talk among themselves and said, let's go have a look at what's going on in Chelm.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Maybe we can stop over here, instead of going to Lublin.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So they got down to Chelm, and they found a few rooms.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I got a little room.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Paid some money to the thing, to get in-- some key money.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we left the train.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we settled down in Chelm.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Did you make any attempt to contact your family?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was nobody to contact to.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "SS ?]-- Later on, we found out what happened to them.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because up until '41, till-- till the Germans attacked, we had regular correspondence with them in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We were sending them parcels of food and other things, and they are sending us letters.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There was no problem, because German and the Soviet Union were at this time Allies.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So they had to pretend that everything is normal.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we got letters.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
